title: Kubernetes: Pods Memory Resources
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors the pods' memory usage inside a namespace of a Kubernetes node.

item:
 The namespace whose memory resources are monitored

discovery:
 One service is created for each namespace.
